EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   02 THRU 10 JUL:

   B. WITHIN 23 MILES OF 57-33.9N 010-16.1W.

   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON

2. CANCEL THIS MSG 101900Z JUL 15.
